你賠啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我不符合418，我一星期返唔夠18小時。"},{"pid":"7a5daf5780b14c6c8b737b97fc20fdf6ac0c8430","tid":449511,"uid":70954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>418好似都要通知期 只係無晒福利<br />\n你賠啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我不符合418，我一星期返唔夠18小時。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n418 連續性合約係講緊啲年假福利<br />\nResign唔關到唔到418事<br />\n如果合約簽左7日通知期而你又真係無翻工<br />\n就賠錢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7959fe33381487fe281c7d3c826b740e93211191","tid":449511,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:00:47.000Z","msg":"比人blacklist就蠢喇"},{"pid":"8014e6d8f68cd9e85b477be57570af56309ee089","tid":449511,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>418好似都要通知期 只係無晒福利<br />\n你賠啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我不符合418，我一星期返唔夠18小時。</blockquote><br />\n都要通知，418係福利標準"},{"pid":"aada4178fb66bf4c8ea6b6f96a81f4f658699692","tid":449511,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2F09.pdf&d=MX0V4rhuZCBpOgK%2F7GxHbMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6e1205e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n* 無試用期/ 完成試用期的非連續性合約，所需的通知期則為議定的期限，而相應的代通知金見表二。<br />\n<br />\n有D交帶提早少少講唔做好難咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2599d7c13db08cb62b0016607ff7516a94e2f331","tid":449511,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>418好似都要通知期 只係無晒福利<br />\n你賠啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我不符合418，我一星期返唔夠18小時。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n418 連續性合約係講緊啲年假福利<br />\nResign唔關到唔到418事<br />\n如果合約簽左7日通知期而你又真係無翻工<br />\n就賠錢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連勞工處咁易都唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8abde7d35cfe3251b353148e391b022779d061e","tid":449511,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:58:47.000Z","msg":"交最低工資就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bc5a87d56aa0a9571dea708aba40392da82362","tid":449511,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52a8d2ed02c3896c29f649b8db322d55e37d3379","tid":449511,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:56:36.000Z","msg":"通唔通知關418咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6fed868509950102c3d1edc9bbc29f236ac137","tid":449511,"uid":133776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:18:37.000Z","msg":"俾錢啦仲上黎問，大公司唔會死錯人，你估差你果幾舊水真係咁緊要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}